38:57.502 --> 38:58.868
I don't know what I am.

39:00.771 --> 39:02.739
Well, you're the daughter
of the man

39:02.741 --> 39:04.040
That runs
the top secret organization

39:04.042 --> 39:05.742
That made your friend
kill a man for some reason

39:05.744 --> 39:08.011
Having to do with your
ex-boyfriend, the president.

39:08.013 --> 39:09.979
(chuckles)

39:09.981 --> 39:12.449
Look, uh...

39:13.884 --> 39:15.018
Hey, hey.

39:15.020 --> 39:16.986
Come on. Don't cry.

39:16.988 --> 39:18.621
I'm not crying.

39:18.623 --> 39:22.459
I'm trying
not to scream.

39:23.928 --> 39:26.663
(breathing heavily)

39:26.665 --> 39:28.365
(gasps)

39:30.801 --> 39:32.001
(whispers) I'm scared.

39:32.003 --> 39:34.070
Okay.

39:34.072 --> 39:36.139
(sets down glass)

39:36.141 --> 39:37.674
Put your head right here.

39:37.676 --> 39:39.376
(laughs)

39:39.378 --> 39:43.646
(chuckles)
come on. Do it.

39:45.116 --> 39:46.916
Do it.

39:46.918 --> 39:49.152
(sighs)

39:49.154 --> 39:50.553
(whispers) there.

39:50.555 --> 39:52.422
(sighs)

39:54.492 --> 39:56.893
You're not alone in this.

39:56.895 --> 39:59.396
I'm not going anywhere.

40:06.070 --> 40:08.605
I'm not going anywhere.

40:35.566 --> 40:36.900
(cell phone rings)

40:36.902 --> 40:38.034
(exhales)

40:38.036 --> 40:40.703
Don't answer it.
(exhales)

40:40.705 --> 40:42.038
(ring)

40:42.040 --> 40:43.473
Um...

40:43.475 --> 40:45.442
(exhales)

40:45.444 --> 40:48.645
(ring)

40:48.647 --> 40:51.147
It could be important.

40:51.149 --> 40:53.082
(ring)

40:53.084 --> 40:54.217
(beep)

40:54.219 --> 40:55.618
Mr. President.

40:55.620 --> 40:57.454
Why so formal?

40:57.456 --> 40:59.055
What can I do for you?

40:59.057 --> 41:00.623
Do for me?

41:00.625 --> 41:02.425
Does everything have to be
transactional in this town?

41:02.427 --> 41:03.860
Even with us?

41:03.862 --> 41:05.662
What happened? Rough day?

41:05.664 --> 41:08.097
You could say that.
How are you?

41:08.099 --> 41:13.203
I'm fine. You're, uh...
Are you okay?

41:18.142 --> 41:20.777
(exhales)

41:20.779 --> 41:22.645
I don't know how to answer that.

41:22.647 --> 41:25.215
I honestly don't.

41:25.217 --> 41:26.950
You sound...

41:26.952 --> 41:28.518
(jake) more wine?

41:31.489 --> 41:33.223
You have company.
Yes.

41:33.225 --> 41:34.691
Explains the formality.

41:34.693 --> 41:36.125
Sorry, it's just--
you should go.

41:36.127 --> 41:37.861
It's okay.
You have company.

41:37.863 --> 41:39.162
We can talk.

41:39.164 --> 41:40.864
That would be rude.

41:40.866 --> 41:43.166
Good-bye, olivia.
(cell phone beeps)

41:43.168 --> 41:45.835
(beep)

41:59.183 --> 42:01.885
We're here, sir.

42:13.564 --> 42:14.764
What the hell is this?

42:14.766 --> 42:17.066
This is a reunion--

42:17.068 --> 42:18.902
One that is long overdue.

42:23.674 --> 42:25.074
(projector and camera shutter
click)
